reviews.text: It was such good value and such a tasty cooking experience

I rarely eat roast meat. In order to write food reviews, I came to this restaurant to eat roast meat. Honestly,  its roast meat is not as good as the Korean restaurant. Prices range from HK$119 to 189. Quite expensive. A set lunch consists of main course, soup, rice, salad and drinks for HK$129. In addition, the restaurant charges a 10% service charge. Very expensive. The environment is good here. The waiter's attitude is very attentive and polite.
Best restaurant ever
Price and quality not balance, please improve
Cheap price with good quality and also not a lot of wait time
